<title>Suggested Sequencing</title>
<para id="fs-idm360764688">Use this narrative with <link class="target-chapter" document="m84519">The Cuban Missile Crisis</link> Narrative and the <link class="target-chapter" document="m84540">John F. Kennedy, Inaugural Address, January 20, 1961</link> Primary Source to cover President Kennedyâ€™s inauguration and his approach to the United Statesâ€™ relationship with the Soviet Union.</para>
